room_title: Escape room "The Atlantis Treasure Hunt" by Codebreakers in Oceanside
room_address: 2401 Vista Way, Suite F, Oceanside, CA 92054
room_description: Journey aboard the pirate ship, to search for the lost city of Atlantis. Players will have fun working with their team to discover the hidden treasure maps and decipher the clues. Try to find the treasure before the pirates find you!
